Zakari Gourouza (amụrụ ya na 8 June 1982) bụ onye judo Nijeria si Dosso
Ọ na-asọ mpi na ụdị ụmụ nwoke 60 kilogram
Na  Summer Olympics nke afọ 2012, onye Russia Arsen Galstyan meriri ya na agba nke abụọ, onye ga-emeri ọla edo na ihe omume ahụ, ebe ọ meriri onye Honduras Kenny Godoy na agba nke mbụ
Zakari Gourouza bụ onye egwuregwu Naijiria mbụ na-asọmpi na egwuregwu nke afọ 2012 nke London.
